How to enter various non-ASCII characters in editors

vim users see :help digraph-table
    
    Unicode     ASCII           key sequence
    char        fallback    vim         emacs            

    «           <<          ^k < <      C-x 8 <
    »           >>          ^k > >      C-x 8 >
    ¥           Y           ^k Y e      C-x 8 Y

